description: Deletes a branch from a repository, unless that branch is the default branch for the repository.

parameters.name: repositoryName
parameters.description: The name of the repository that contains the branch to be deleted.

parameters.name: branchName
parameters.description: The name of the branch to delete.

nested_items.name: deletedBranch
nested_items.description: Information about the branch deleted by the operation, including the branch name and the commit ID that was the tip of the branch.

nested_items.name: commitId
nested_items.description: The ID of the last commit made to the branch.
